snippet.title: Mechanized Super Mario Bros. U - City Trailer
snippet.description:
Livin in the City, you know, you have to survive!

This trailer was originally part of the New Super Mario Bros. U Modding Direct from November 18. 2022!  Check it out:  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vwak5DkfsMw

Infos:
Mechanized Super Mario Bros. U is a New Super Mario Bros. U Mod, heavily inspired by Kirby: Planet Robobot. It will contain two Worlds full of new, interesting Level with an overall mechanical Theme. The mod is slated to release early next Year.

Features:

- 17 New Levels
- New Backgrounds
- New Tilesets
- Collectable Code Cubes
- Custom Music, mostly from Kirby
